title: Spanish Mediterranean villages-built community- Westchase
posting_body: For leasing info call or text
Wrapped in the same earth-tone hues, inviting charm and soft ambience of Spanish Mediterranean villages-built centuries ago, this community presents a modern menu of new world luxuries.
The first component of the West 8 master plan, this community provides the personal privacy of a great residential address within an urban utopia that feels more like an old world neighborhood.
Enveloped by stately Live Oak trees, this community promises a lifestyle that is, literally, made in the shade.
Grand fireplace and great room lounge
WaterWorks pool, hot tub and showers
